xxl.core.spatial.cursors
Class Replicator.QueueEl

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.spatial.cursors.Replicator.QueueEl
Enclosing class:
Replicator
protected static class Replicator.QueueEl
extends Object

A Wrapper-class needed to unwind the recursive split. We do not use "real" recursion here for reasons of flexibility: the type of Queue used determines the traversing- strategy of recursive splits.
